    <thetext>False resource leak warning:

try (ByteArrayOutputStream baos = new ByteArrayOutputStream()) {
  for (;;) {
    return;
  }
} catch (Exception e) {
}

Same code but no warning:

try (ByteArrayOutputStream baos = new ByteArrayOutputStream()) {
  while (true) {
    return;
  }
} catch (Exception e) {
}</thetext>
